                  </span>
                  <input id="hw-share-copy-link-text" type="text" value="{{ sigma_proxy_url }}" title="Copy link" readonly="" data-modal-id="group-share-popup" />
                  <input id="hw-share-copied-flag" type="text" value="0" />
                  <div id="hw-share-copy-link-copied" class="hw-share-copy-link-copied">✓</div>
                </div>
                <div class="a2a_modal_body a2a_menu a2a-thanks" id="thanks">
                  <div class="a2a_localize" data-a2a-localize="inner,ThanksForSharing">Thanks for sharing!</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="hw-share-tooltip-text-wrap">
            <p><span class="hw-proxy-text-underline">To share with users that are connected to the institution’s/school’s network:</span>  Click &lt;<strong>Link</strong>&gt; button to copy the content permanent URL.</p> <br />
            <p>
						  <span class="hw-proxy-text-underline">To share a link in a Learning Management System (LMS) course (such as Blackboard, Canvas, Moodle, etc.) that will work for remote users as well as those connected to the school’s network:</span>
              <ol>
                <li><p>1. Contact <a href="mailto:customersuccess@bpseducation.com" >customersuccess@bpseducation.com </a> to confirm that your LMS has been set up correctly in our system. </p></li>
                <ul><li>- Provide your school name and the link for your course in the email.</li></ul>
                <li>2. Click &lt;<strong>Link</strong>&gt; button to copy the content permanent URL and paste into your course.</li>
              </ol>
            </p><br />
            <p><span class="hw-proxy-text-underline">To share with remote users:</span> Click &lt;<strong>Proxy Link</strong>&gt; button to copy the content permanent URL with the added prefix for your institution's/school’s proxy server that will prompt users to log-in with their institution/school credentials in order to gain access to the content.</p>
          </div><br />
          <a class="a2a_button_copy_link" target="" href="{{ link_url }}" rel="nofollow noopener">
            <span class="a2a_s_link a2a_img_text hw-share-link-only">Link</span>
          </a> <br />
          <a class="link-proxy" target="" href="{{ sigma_proxy_url }}" rel="nofollow noopener">
            <span class="a2a_s_link a2a_img_text hw-share-proxy-link">Proxy Link</span>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
        <div class="proxy-wrap">
          <div class="hw-share-proxy-modal">
            <div class="a2a_overlay" id="hw-share-proxy-overlay" ></div>
            <div id="hw-share-proxy-modal" class="a2a_modal" role="dialog" tabindex="-1" aria-label="Copy link">
              <div class="a2a_modal_body a2a_menu" id="hw-share-copy-link">
                <span id="hw-share-link-icon" class="a2a_svg a2a_s_link">
                  <svg focusable="false" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 32 32">
